Class BigNum

  • java.lang.Object
    • BigNum

  • public class BigNum
extends java.lang.Object
    The BigNum class represents any length non-negative integer, and supports basic operations on them. BigNum objects are immutable.
    Version:
    Feb 6, 2015
    Author:
    Ted Krovetz, Brandon Byrne
